<A>__{rear angle of agnis, crouching in the lightly falling snow. at the edge of the sea. the spot where she once sent her dog to rest. hear footfalls crunching slowly across the rocks. a bulky figure comes into frame. crouches down beside her. close. she stares at the gray horizon.}
<C>__{quoyle }
<D>__{mavis bangs. told me where you'd be.}
<A>__{no answer. but she hears him all right.}
